Package ualberta.g12.adventurecreator.data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdventureCreator
    Application object for the Application.
    Choice
    Used to implement, set, and link desired choices to each other.
    FModel<V extends FView>
    The Model that all Fragment Models must extend.
    Fragment
    A Fragment has a title, used to identify the fragment to the user, and a list of FragmentParts.
    FragmentPart
    A FragmentPart can represent different forms of content for a Fragment.
    LModel<V extends LView>
    All StoryList models adhere to this class.
    OfflineIOHelper
    Will Handle loading and saving of our offline(cached) stories from local storage.
    SModel<V extends SView<SModel>>
    A Model class that all Story Model Classes should extend.
    Story
    Models a story that would be created by an Author.
    StoryList
    Models the list of stories.
